HEADWORD: Malison
<hw>Mal"i*son</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>maleicon</ets>, L. <ets>maledictio</ets>. See <er>Malediction</er>,
and cf. <er>Benison</er>.]</ety> <def>Malediction; curse;
execration.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>God's <qex>malison</qex> on his head who this gainsays.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Malkin</ent>⟦br⟧
